<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Theadelphia</placeName></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><div n="ctr" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/><expan>π<ex cert="high">αρὰ</ex></expan> Ἀλυπίου 

    <lb n="2"/>ἐπεὶ φροντίδα ποιοῦμαι <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τῶ</supplied>ν διαφερόντων 

    <lb n="3"/><choice><corr>ἡμῖν</corr><sic>ημειν</sic></choice> ἐν τῇ Σαθρώ, ἔμ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">θ</supplied>ον δὲ παρὰ Σύρου ἐν-

    <lb n="4"/>λιπές τι ἔργον εἶναι ἐν τῇ διώρυχι πρὸς τοῖς 

    <lb n="5"/>ζυγώμασιν, χρῄζειν τε τὸ ἔργον ἀνάγ-

    <lb n="6"/>κης, ἀπέστειλα πρὸς ὑμᾶς στρατιώτην, 

    <lb n="7"/><hi rend="diaeresis">ἵ</hi>να ἀπὸ τῶν ὠφελουμένων πάντων 

    <lb n="8"/>ἡ ἐργατεία βληθῇ καὶ ταχέως τὸ ἔργον 

    <lb n="9"/>γένηται πρὶν τοῦ ποτισμοῦ τοῦ 

    <lb n="10"/>κατεπείγοντος πρὸς τὸ εὐμαρῶς τὰ 

    <lb n="11"/>ὕδατα πάντας ἡμᾶς ἔχειν, ἀλλὰ 

    <lb n="12"/>καί, εἴ τι δέοιτο, ἐν τῇ καινῇ διώρυχι 

    <lb n="13"/>καὶ ἐν τῇ κωμητικῇ γένηται <hi rend="diaeresis">ἵ</hi>να 

    <lb n="14"/>πανταχόθεν τὰ ὕδατα ἔχειν 

    <lb n="15"/>δυνηθῆτε, τὴν δὲ δαπά-

    <lb n="16"/>νην τοῦ στρα<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τιώτου</supplied> καθὼς 

    <lb n="17"/>ἔθος ἐστὶν ὑμῖν παράσχετε. ἐρρῶ-

    <lb n="18"/>σθαί σε εὔχο-

    <lb n="19"/>μαι 

    <lb n="20"/><expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="9"><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">θ</unclear></num> Θὼθ <num value="3"><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">γ</unclear></num> Ἡρωνείνῳ <expan>φρον<ex cert="high">τιστῇ</ex></expan> <expan>Σαθ<ex cert="high">ρώ</ex></expan>. 
</ab></div><div n="ms" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="21"/><expan>π<ex cert="high">αρὰ</ex></expan> Ἀλυπίου Ἡρωνείνῳ <expan><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">φρον</unclear><ex cert="high">τιστῇ</ex></expan> <expan><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">Σαθ<ex cert="high">ρώ</ex></supplied></expan>. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.12881" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.12881" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="257" notBefore="257" type="textDate" value="0257-08-31">31. Aug. 257</date></p></div><div n="meta.12881" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Gehört zum Heroninos - Archiv. Zur Datierung vgl. BL VIII, S. 289; Rathbone, Economic Rationalism. S. 222 und ZPE 150, 2004, S. 208f.</p></div><div n="meta.12881" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Rein.</title><biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">115</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">12881</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0195</series>; <biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">115</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0195;2;115" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.12881" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">289</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.12881" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.12881" org="uniform" p